message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the sub-category for Sound and Music Computing, which is the main topic of this paper. Other possible sub-categories could include cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) since the paper uses deep neural networks for enhancement. cs.SI (Signal Processing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) could also be possible sub-categories since the paper deals with audio signal processing and uses neural networks for enhancement.
